#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_acknowledgement/email/body.html:40
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_acknowledgement/email/body.txt:9
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:98
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:26
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.html:63
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.txt:15
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.html:62
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:15
